      • addLocationsToLocation

        public void addLocationsToLocation(Point location)
        The method is used to add a serial of locations into the path list. If the parameter location is not adjacent to the last point of the path, the points between them will be added in the method.
        Parameters:
        location - the new point which should be add into the path.
